-- Ciel Textile Rises Most in 8 Months in Port Louis Trading
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-03-08T08:33:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-08/ciel-textile-rises-most-in-8-months-in-port-louis-trading.html
Ciel Textile Ltd. (FKL) , a Mauritian
apparels company with operations in Madagascar and  Asia , rose
the most in more than eight months.  The stock  gained 4.2 percent, or 0.6 rupee, the biggest
intraday gain since June 24, to 15 rupees by 12:10 p.m. in  Port
Louis , the capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
